<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَإِن كَانَ اثْنَيْنِ يُسمى عَزِيزًا<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>الْمَشْهُور<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَإِن كَانُوا أَكثر يُسمى مَشْهُورا ومستفيضا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>